title: I Came Face To Face With Indias Deadliest Predator. #wildlife #animals

author: Forrest Galante
description:
These are India's 10 deadliest animals, all found at Vantara!

Vantara is not a zoo, it is a wildlife rescue and rehabilitation center dedicated to preserving animals from all over the world. Thank you to Anant Ambani for his dedication to conservation and allowing us to visit and showcase his beautiful facility. 

Forrest Galante is a world renowned wildlife biologist and TV Host. His mission is to inspire and educate people about animals and adventure through the media, including hosting programs on Discovery Channel, on-camera expert interviews, and production of his own wildlife and natural history shows.
